            "title": "NBA｜76人明星中鋒安比膝傷提早收咧",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"76人明星中鋒安比膝傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f8f7d710216b46b4c6735b7efcf742f3/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030115475362426.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">76人明星中鋒安比膝傷提早收咧。REUTERS</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>76人明星中鋒安比（Joel Embiid）近年一直受到傷患困擾，球會周五又宣布這名當家球星因為左膝傷患而提早收咧，令到目前於東岸排12位的76人爭奪季後賽形勢急轉直下。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ebb961383c8107bd357d201377096326/2025-03/2025-02-09T202750Z_1247035421_MT1USATODAY25378086_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-MILWAUKEE-BUCKS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c6948f5e4afe30e0689d740052ebc17/2025-03/2025-02-13T032811Z_584343067_MT1USATODAY25403112_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-BROOKLYN-NETS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c1a31062fe409bea29c28fb394f09ab6/2025-03/2025-02-13T032839Z_1352608498_MT1USATODAY25403113_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-BROOKLYN-NETS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保羅佐治(右)今季亦因傷缺陣19場。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"保羅佐治(圖)今季加盟76人與安比合作。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99723a5dd467aeae7c7ed49958f8acca/2025-03/2025-02-13T033930Z_128093478_MT1USATODAY25403216_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-BROOKLYN-NETS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        保羅佐治(圖)今季加盟76人與安比合作。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b282c76a29bef5072760fec97f075bde/2025-03/2025-02-09T202732Z_577451212_MT1USATODAY25378081_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-MILWAUKEE-BUCKS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a6decede401b7e7a201271491b250fb8/2025-03/2025-02-09T202745Z_1271993834_MT1USATODAY25378084_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-MILWAUKEE-BUCKS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(中)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ea4ba4a166f72a69472483f4b76cc7e0/2025-03/2025-02-09T210048Z_766783672_MT1USATODAY25378214_RTRMADP_3_NBA-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS-AT-MILWAUKEE-BUCKS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(中)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/ce162cd123ad19a03c474a54d54cc973/2025-03/2025-02-21T011933Z_1808773574_MT1USATODAY25466952_RTRMADP_3_NBA-BOSTON-CELTICS-AT-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/332b77a17285d662f4538ad159390146/2025-03/2025-02-23T010557Z_719854750_MT1USATODAY25486758_RTRMADP_3_NBA-BROOKLYN-NETS-AT-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(右)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f28a986c8d080b2eaada370ff7c83359/2025-03/2025-02-23T033626Z_1262610865_MT1USATODAY25489556_RTRMADP_3_NBA-BROOKLYN-NETS-AT-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d1b3d62ecf971681ea2cd6a3bc590bc5/2025-03/2025-02-23T033604Z_818190787_MT1USATODAY25489548_RTRMADP_3_NBA-BROOKLYN-NETS-AT-PHILADELPHIA-76ERS.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        76人中鋒安比(左)因傷提早收咧。REUTERS\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>安比膝傷提早收咧</h2>\n<p>76人今季簽下NBA名星賽後衛保羅佐治（Paul George）與安比合作，目標直指NBA總冠軍。可惜，兩人今季都受到傷患問題嚴重影響上陣時間，直接拖累球隊成績；76人最近常規賽便遭逢9連敗，以20勝38負排東岸第12位。周五76人再官方宣布安比收咧的惡號：「安比接受新一輪檢查，經過醫療團隊開會後斷定他因為膝部傷患要缺席球季餘下的比賽！」嚴重打擊球隊爭奪季後賽席位。\n\n</p><h2>手術後休息不足以致舊患復發</h2>\n<p>安比去年2月才接受了膝部半月板手術，當時只休息了兩個月於4月便急急復出；夏天又代表美國出戰巴黎奧運並奪金牌而回。相信是休息不足以致他今季又再舊患復發，斷斷續續只上陣了19場，早前他便承認因為手術後養傷時間不足，以致一直未能完全康復。至於今季加盟76人的保羅佐治情況亦好不多，常規賽58場已經有19次缺陣。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
